                    h2.headline-2.ff-sans-hl.p-color Basilisk
                    p Basilisk is a complementary product to HydraDX launched on Kusama.
                    ul.listing
                        li.listing__item Supporting the long tail of cryptoassets and experimenting with financial applications and governance
                        li.listing__item Bootstrap token liquidity to life with our improved Liquidity Bootstrapping Pool module.
                .basilisk-support.text-center
                    h3.fw-normal
